d this myself, but I took my new Druid into Paludal last night at 12 and passed a lot of green mobs at the entrance from Shadeweaver's Thicket. You will need PoK to get to the Shar Vahl side or a map and a decent invis to run through from the Shadow Haven entrance, and some money to buy spells as all you'll really get here is fast XP and a few gold.<br>
<br>
With PoK, take the portal to Shar Vahl, then turn left and run past the tents until you find the path leading down the hill from the entrance to the city. Follow that down the hill and out until it branches to the right, then invis and follow that branch... after a couple of minutes that ends at a tunnel leading down. Go down the tunnel and find the Paludal entrance; I think it's first left, first right, first right, but you'd be best to print out a map to take with you.<br>
<br>
Once you zone in, start killing <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   . The bugs near the zone line should be dark blue, and as they go light blue you can move further in to find their higher-level relatives... you may even be able to start further in as I could kill yellows and some reds at this level in Nektulos. Most bugs that I killed in that area could be single-pulled, just watch out for the wandering adds. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ailurya@themagicianstower>Ailurya</A> at: 2/11/03 1:16:04 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=barmodius>Barmodius</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 77<br> <font color=#333333>(2/11/03 1:48:03 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm39.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=23.topic&index=1>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Paludal</span><hr size=1> The little mushrooms are good too, and they aren't social like the bugs.<br>
<br>
I brought my wee enchanter here and leveled from 9-12.  Good, safe XP.  No fiends roam near the cave to SV, so the only worry is social adds when fighting the bugs. <p><div align="center"> <a href="#"><img src="http://www.nemeandesign.net/eq/sig2.jpg" width="382" height="66" border="0" onClick="window.open('http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=528641', 'morillion', 'WIDTH=800,HEIGHT=600')"></a> </p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ailurya@themagicianstower>Ailurya</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 42<br> <font color=#333333>(2/11/03 2:18:22 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm39.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=23.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Paludal</span><hr size=1> Good point, I'd forgotten about the shrooms. Didn't realise they weren't social, I'd been fighting shrooms in DSP with my Monk earlier and they'd definitely come running to help if I pulled one. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ailurya@themagicianstower>Ailurya</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 68<br> <font color=#333333>(2/24/03 11:25:34 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm39.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=23.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Paludal</span><hr size=1> Actually, I took my new Chanter here at level 6 yesterday and was fighting the mobs right after the zone line. They were white to yellow initially, and, needless to say, yellow mobs at level 6 in Paludal give a lot of XP <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  . AFAIR I was getting about a whole yellow of XP per kill at that level and the wanderer near the zone was spawning fast enough that I was just back to max mana and hit points ready for the next fight... quite often it didn't hit me bad enough that I had to sit and wait for it to respawn, so I could pull one of the others further in before that.<br>
<br>
The problem for a Mage is that the first three spawns were close enough together that pulling one brings all three, and three yellow-con mobs will kill you fast. As a Chanter I was able to Lull two so that I'd usually only get one mob, but by level 8 I suspect that the Mage pet could tank long enough for you to kill what will then be three dark blues. Or bring someone who can Lull/Mez the mobs at a lower level and you'll probably get XP even faster as a duo. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ailurya@themagicianstower>Ailurya</A> at: 2/24/03 11:26:14 am<br></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm39.showNextMessage?topicID=23.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm39.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=23.topic&index=3><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm39.threadControl?topicID=23.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/unread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm39.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=23.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm39.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=23.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub102.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName>